  classDef decide fill:#1c8a57,stroke:#11623e,color:#fff,rx:8,ry:8;
  classDef perform fill:#d07a22,stroke:#9a5510,color:#fff,rx:8,ry:8;

  class I1,I2,I3 input;
  class R recommend;
  class A agree;
  class D decide;
  class P perform;
```

